ARRANGE-NUMBERS

NAME
	Arrange-Numbers
	
DESCRIPTION

	The classic game of arrange numbers implemented for android 
	operational systems. It was written in Java using the Android SDK.

	This implementation uses the BaseAdapter Class with GridViews, 
	Buttons and XML templates.

USAGE

	 For a simple view test, fork this repository and run it on an ADT or
	 android device running the Android 2.1 version (Eclair). It was the 
	 development and testing version. 

SEE ALSO

	http://developer.android.com/index.html
	http://code.google.com/android/

AUTHOR
	Written by Gustavo Pantuza

